.class);\\n        writer.name(\\\"generated-value\\\")\\n                .count(3)\\n                .enabled(true)\\n                .type(String.class);\\n\\n        JAnnotationUse annotationUse = writer.getAnnotationUse();\\n        assertThat(annotationUse.getAnnotationMembers()).containsOnlyKeys(\\\"name\\\", \\\"count\\\", \\\"enabled\\\", \\\"type\\\");\\n\\n        ByteArrayOutputStream output = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\\n        codeModel.build(new SingleStreamCodeWriter(output));\\n        String generatedSource = output.toString(StandardCharsets.UTF_8);\\n\\n        assertThat(generatedSource)\\n                .contains(\\\"@TypedAnnotationWriterTest.SampleAnnotation\\\")\\n                .contains(\\\"name = \\\\\\\"generated-value\\\\\\\"\\\")\\n                .contains(\\\"count = 3\\\")\\n                .contains(\\\"enabled = true\\\")\\n                .contains(\\\"type = String.class\\\");\\n    }\\n\\n    public @interface SampleAnnotation {\\n        String name();\\n\\n        int count();\\n\\n        boolean enabled();\\n\\n        Class<?> type();\\n    }\\n\\n    public interface SampleAnnotationWriter extends JAnnotationWriter<SampleAnnotation> {\\n        SampleAnnotationWriter name(String value);\\n\\n        SampleAnnotationWriter count(int value);\\n\\n        SampleAnnotationWriter enabled(boolean value);\\n\\n        SampleAnnotationWriter type(Class<?> value);\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}\n1702:[tool-call] end id=call_vRoyJyhmDJ0shCV64UOJt5oN|fc_013332e1445e75730169f5d746fc7c8197b2b81b6d80177ef3 name=write args={\"path\": \"tests/src/org.glassfish.jaxb/codemodel/4.0.6/src/test/java/org_glassfish_jaxb/codemodel/TypedAnnotationWriterTest.java\", \"content\": \"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npackage org_glassfish_jaxb.codemodel;\\n\\nimport static org.asser